38#include "gen_locl.h"

40__RCSID("$NetBSD: gen_glue.c,v 1.2 2017/01/28 21:31:45 christos Exp $");
41
42static void
43generate_2int (const Type *t, const char *gen_name)
44{
45 Member *m;
46
47 fprintf (headerfile,
48 "unsigned %s2int(%s);\n",
49 gen_name, gen_name);
50
51 fprintf (codefile,
52 "unsigned %s2int(%s f)\n"
53 "{\n"
54 "unsigned r = 0;\n",
55 gen_name, gen_name);
56
57 ASN1_TAILQ_FOREACH(m, t->members, members) {
58 fprintf (codefile, "if(f.%s) r |= (1U << %d);\n",
59 m->gen_name, m->val);
60 }
61 fprintf (codefile, "return r;\n"
62 "}\n\n");
63}
64
65static void
66generate_int2 (const Type *t, const char *gen_name)
67{
68 Member *m;
69
70 fprintf (headerfile,
71 "%s int2%s(unsigned);\n",
72 gen_name, gen_name);
73
74 fprintf (codefile,
75 "%s int2%s(unsigned n)\n"
76 "{\n"
77 "\t%s flags;\n\n"
78 "\tmemset(&flags, 0, sizeof(flags));\n\n",
79 gen_name, gen_name, gen_name);
80
81 if(t->members) {
82 ASN1_TAILQ_FOREACH(m, t->members, members) {
83 fprintf (codefile, "\tflags.%s = (n >> %d) & 1;\n",
84 m->gen_name, m->val);
85 }
86 }
87 fprintf (codefile, "\treturn flags;\n"
88 "}\n\n");
89}
90
91/*
92 * This depends on the bit string being declared in increasing order
93 */
94
95static void
96generate_units (const Type *t, const char *gen_name)
97{
98 Member *m;
99
100 if (template_flag) {
101 fprintf (headerfile,
102 "extern const struct units *asn1_%s_table_units;\n",
103 gen_name);
104 fprintf (headerfile, "#define asn1_%s_units() (asn1_%s_table_units)\n",
105 gen_name, gen_name);
106 } else {
107 fprintf (headerfile,
108 "const struct units * asn1_%s_units(void);\n",
109 gen_name);
110 }
111
112 fprintf (codefile,
113 "static struct units %s_units[] = {\n",
114 gen_name);
115
116 if(t->members) {
117 ASN1_TAILQ_FOREACH_REVERSE(m, t->members, memhead, members) {
118 fprintf (codefile,
119 "\t{\"%s\",\t1U << %d},\n", m->name, m->val);
120 }
121 }
122
123 fprintf (codefile,
124 "\t{NULL,\t0}\n"
125 "};\n\n");
126
127 if (template_flag)
128 fprintf (codefile,
129 "const struct units * asn1_%s_table_units = %s_units;\n",
130 gen_name, gen_name);
131 else
132 fprintf (codefile,
133 "const struct units * asn1_%s_units(void){\n"
134 "return %s_units;\n"
135 "}\n\n",
136 gen_name, gen_name);
137
138
139}
140
141void
142generate_glue (const Type *t, const char *gen_name)
143{
144 switch(t->type) {
145 case TTag:
146 generate_glue(t->subtype, gen_name);
147 break;
148 case TBitString :
149 if (!ASN1_TAILQ_EMPTY(t->members)) {
150 generate_2int (t, gen_name);
151 generate_int2 (t, gen_name);
152 if (parse_units_flag)
153 generate_units (t, gen_name);
154 }
155 break;
156 default :
157 break;
158 }
159}
